Package: ChIASim
Type: Package
Title: ChIASim
Version: 1.2
Author: Shuyuan Lou (The Ohio State University, USA), Shili Lin (The Ohio State University, USA)
Maintainer: Shuyuan Lou <lou.59@osu.edu>
Description: ChIASim implements a realistic simulation algorithm designed to generate in silico ChIA-PET, PLAC-seq or Hi-ChIP data by mimicking the major steps of such experiments. 
